    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Prerequisite: Copy Techinque </p><p>When you are in danger, your Old Friend goes berserk.</p><p> While your Old Friend is active or when you activate it while under 50% Hit Points, your Old Friend activates at Stage 3.</p><p> When it does, you must make a Charisma Check vs DC 20.</p><p> On a failure, the Old Friend gains an additional 4 ASI and cannot be controlled by you.</p><p> While this is active, the Old Friend will be in the DM's control and is under the effects of the Berserk condition targetting hostile creatures.</p><p> When all hostiles are defeated, the Old Friend will treat the creature closest to you as a Hostile.</p><p> On a success, the Old Friend gains an additional 4 ASI and can be controlled as normal.</p><p> If your Old Friend is Berserk, as an action you may remake the check.</p><p> ON a success, the Old Friend immediately deactivates.</p><p></p>",
